articles.author: Peggy Hollinger, Clive Cookson
articles.title: ESA aims to send astronauts to Moon on European rocket - Financial Times
articles.description: ESA director-general outlines plan to develop independent human launch capability within a decade
articles.content: The European Space Agency is drawing up proposals to develop spacecraft over the next decade that could fly ESA astronauts into orbit and to the Moon, according to its director-general Josef Aschbach… [+3847 chars]
